author: Aya Batrawy | AP
title: World G20 leaders in video call to coordinate virus response
description: Leaders of the world's most powerful economies have convened virtually to coordinate a response to the fast-spreading coronavirus
content:
The meeting comes amid criticism that the worlds wealthiest countries have not taken enough action to combat the virus or its economic impact globally as people lose their incomes due to closures, curfews and lockdowns.
